---
import Base from "@layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "@components/Header.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — saralogy.com"
  description="Privacy policy and data protection information for saralogy.com. GDPR compliant."
  noIndex={true}
>
  <Header />

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

    <section class="pt-16 pb-10 border-b border-gray-100">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Last updated: June 2026
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 space-y-12">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          saralogy.com is a personal website operated by Berk Saraloglu. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          This site is compliant with the GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation). Your privacy is important to us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Collection</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Google Analytics 4</h3>
            <p>This site uses Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors use the site. Data is collected only with your explicit consent via the cookie consent banner at the bottom of the page.</p>
            <p class="mt-2">GA4 collects: page views, scroll depth, click events, referral source, device type, and approximate geographic location (country/city level).</p>
            <p class="mt-2">We do NOT track: personally identifiable information (name, email, phone number, IP address beyond city level).</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cookies</h3>
            <p>This site uses one functional cookie: `cookie_consent`, which stores your preference (accepted or rejected) for analytics. This cookie is set for 365 days.</p>
            <p class="mt-2">No tracking cookies are set unless you consent to analytics.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Contact Forms</h3>
            <p>This site does not have contact forms. To reach Berk, visit the <a href="/work" class="underline hover:text-gray-900">Work with me</a> page for contact details.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Under the GDPR, you have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for analytics at any time</li>
          <li>Receive a copy of your data in a portable format</li>
          <li>Object to processing</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          To exercise any of these rights, contact Berk by email at <a href="mailto:berksaraloglu@gmail.com?subject=Privacy%20request%20via%20saralogy.com" class="underline hover:text-gray-900">berksaraloglu@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Google Fonts</h3>
            <p>This site loads the Inter font family from Google Fonts. Google processes your IP address and user agent to deliver the font. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-gray-900">Google's privacy policy</a>.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Vercel CDN</h3>
            <p>This site is hosted on Vercel. Vercel processes your IP address and connection metadata to serve the site. See <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-gray-900">Vercel's privacy policy</a>.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">External Links</h3>
            <p>This site links to external sites (LinkedIn, GitHub, Spotify, SoundCloud, etc.). Those sites have their own privacy policies, and we are not responsible for their data practices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Google Analytics data is retained according to Google's default policy (typically 14 months). The cookie consent preference is retained for 365 days.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We do not store personal data from visitors beyond what Google Analytics captures.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Questions?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          If you have questions about this privacy policy or how your data is handled, reach out via <a href="/work" class="underline hover:text-gray-900">the contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

    </section>

  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-gray-100 mt-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:items-center sm:justify-between text-sm text-gray-500">
      <span>© 2026 Berk Saraloglu · AI-native marketing leader in Hamburg</span>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/now" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Now</a>
        <a href="/music" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Music</a>
        <a href="mailto:berksaraloglu@gmail.com?subject=Opportunity%20via%20saralogy.com" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">Email</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/berksaraloglu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/berksaraloglu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>
